<body>
    <div class="header clearfix">

        <img src="../Assets/logo.png" alt="logo">
        <h3>FelIn</h3>
    </div>
    <h2 class="welcome">Welcome to FelIn! Please enter the following information to help us match you with a job.</h2>
    <div class="form">
        <form action="/action_page.php">
            <p class="Questions">General Information</p>
            Full Name: <input type="text" name="Name"><br>
            Location: <input type="text" name="Location"><br>
            Email: <input type="email" name="Email"><br>
            Phone Number: <input type="tel" name="Number"><br>
            Skills (separated by commas): <input type="text" name="Skills"><br>

            <p class="Questions">Password</p>
            Password: <input type="password" name="password"><br>
            Re-enter Password: <input type="password" name="password-confirm"><br>

            Experience: <input type="text" name="Experience"><br><br>
            <p class="Questions">Questions</p>
            1. Tell us about yourself. <textarea type="text" name="About"></textarea><br>
            2. How has being incarcerated changed you? <textarea type="text" name="Change"></textarea><br>
            3. Short/Long term goals? <textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            4. Where do you see yourself in 10 years?<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            5. How do you plan to transition back into daily civilian life?<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            6. Have you completed any unique programs/workshops? If yes, how have they contributed to your personal outlook/attitude?<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            7. Why do you believe you made mistakes in the past and how will you prevent yourself from making mistakes again.<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            8. What activities/hobbies do you plan on taking up outside of work?<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            9. What is your outlook on the criminal justice system?<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>
            10. Is there anything else important that people should know about you?<textarea type="text" name="Problem"></textarea><br>

            <input class="btn-submit" type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form>
    </div>
</body>

